'''Islamic Secondary School Dr. Ahmed Smajlovic''' ({{lang-hr|Islamska Gimnazija dr. Ahmed Smajlović}}, {{lang-bs|Islamska gimnazija dr. Ahmed Smajlović}}) is a private secondary school ([[Gymnasium (school)|gymnasium]]) situated in [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]].<ref name="Yearbook of Muslims in Europe, Volume 7">{{cite web|url=https://books.google.pl/books?id=oQAKDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA155&lpg=PA155&dq=Islamska+Gimnazija+dr.+Ahmed+Smajlovi%C4%87&source=bl&ots=a20Fm32AVQ&sig=J6toWw0AzzHBenJ-igy5JxiphSE&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj2sazAj__MAhVB1ywKHfX1B-kQ6AEIdTAN#v=onepage&q=Islamska%20Gimnazija%20dr.%20Ahmed%20Smajlovi%C4%87&f=false|title=Yearbook of Muslims in Europe, Volume 7|date= |accessdate=29 May 2016}}</ref> Islamic Secondary School Dr. Ahmed Smajlović carries the educational programs of general secondary school direction. Classes are taught in [[Croatian language]].
